Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.74,0:01:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,痴女小姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.78,0:02:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,第一章 办公女性
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.71,0:03:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那个你过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.05,0:03:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.72,0:03:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,最近的数字好像不好看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:04:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,实在抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.73,0:04:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,必须再接再厉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.57,0:04:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.90,0:04:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.57,0:04:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,最近是不是放松了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.24,0:04:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,实往对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这样下去就没有奖金了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.08,0:04:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.09,0:04:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至连工资也成问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.93,0:04:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.44,0:04:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,被教育的时候你眼睛看哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.11,0:04:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,看我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.29,0:05:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚刚不也一直看着我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.30,0:05:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,总是偷偷盯着我看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.64,0:05:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你在胡说什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.83,0:05:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,您不要害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我都知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.01,0:05:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.01,0:05:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你在问我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,办公室里不能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,明明很期待的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.44,0:07:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好变态啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.78,0:07:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,您不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.96,0:07:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都不信任您的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.97,0:08:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,您一直没发现吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.65,0:08:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,一直都不认真工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.65,0:08:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.34,0:08:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.01,0:08:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.35,0:08:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么发抖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.04,0:09:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好臭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.54,0:09:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,败给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.71,0:09:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.09,0:10:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,抖得好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.11,0:10:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.28,0:10:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.29,0:10:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好恶心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.29,0:10:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.48,0:11:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么这么硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.15,0:11:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,因为舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,工作时间居然这样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.19,0:11:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,太有意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.69,0:11:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.03,0:11:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,突然这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.36,0:11:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.04,0:11:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,越摸越硬吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.05,0:12:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.05,0:12:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好变态啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.59,0:12:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,您想摸我的腿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.59,0:12:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.93,0:12:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,想摸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.09,0:12:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.93,0:12:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.93,0:12:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不让你摸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,您在期待什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.95,0:13:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.62,0:13:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,在期待什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.29,0:13:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你要口交吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.46,0:13:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.14,0:13:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好臭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.31,0:13:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.48,0:13:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能会舔的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.00,0:14:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,味道不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.34,0:14:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,想要我怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.68,0:14:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.19,0:14:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你要拜托我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.52,0:14:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,求你舔我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.53,0:14:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.36,0:14:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.39,0:14:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.56,0:14:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,继续舔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你要求我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.57,0:15:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,求你舔到深处
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.60,0:15:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.61,0:16:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你的表情好恶心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.45,0:16:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.36,0:17:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.71,0:17:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,害羞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.54,0:17:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.75,0:18:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,您想要我的腿怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.43,0:18:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,想尽情地摸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.76,0:18:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,想摸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.27,0:18:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那就满足你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.11,0:18:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,想摸我的腿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,真好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.66,0:19:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很想摸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.16,0:19:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.17,0:19:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那就先舔一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.52,0:19:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,还没同意你摸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.69,0:19:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,只能用嘴巴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.86,0:20:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,美味
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.73,0:20:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.23,0:20:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.33,0:22:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.00,0:22:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,超级棒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.84,0:22:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这么喜欢腿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.67,0:22:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.53,0:22:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,奸像什么流出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.36,0:22:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.70,0:22:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好脏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.21,0:23:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,抹到脚上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.71,0:23:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你再舔干净可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.72,0:23:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.57,0:23:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么这么兴奋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.92,0:23:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,想摸我的腿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.09,0:23:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那就让你摸摸
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.30,0:24:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.48,0:24:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,继续
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.73,0:26:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,想直接舔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.40,0:26:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.79,0:27:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.50,0:28:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.36,0:28:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.06,0:28:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你还可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.23,0:29:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.90,0:29:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,部长
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.58,0:29:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.92,0:29:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以摸我了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.25,0:29:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.44,0:29:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,脱掉衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.46,0:30:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.30,0:30:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,只限今日
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.52,0:31:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.70,0:31:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.74,0:31:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.58,0:32:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢腿还是胸
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.60,0:32:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.31,0:33:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好软
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.85,0:33:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,可以舔乳房吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.52,0:33:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你也想舔胸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.03,0:33:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.70,0:34:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.65,0:36:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,请停一下
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.66,0:36:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,您好像在期待什么
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.34,0:36:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.34,0:36:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,希望我怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.18,0:36:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.52,0:36:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不要射在里面哦
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.38,0:37:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么摸我
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.05,0:37:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,控制不住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.56,0:37:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.23,0:37:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.08,0:37:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.83,0:39:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.12,0:41:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,可以亲吻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.45,0:41:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,可以再看看腿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.12,0:41:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,腿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.46,0:41:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.00,0:41:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.90,0:42:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.65,0:44:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,您不要这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.15,0:44:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,从后面进入吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.69,0:44:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.52,0:45:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,再快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.61,0:46:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.31,0:46:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.47,0:47:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.81,0:47:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.60,0:49:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,请您继续吧
