Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.41,1:02:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,说出来
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.58,1:02:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思呢
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.26,1:02:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.59,1:02:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.43,1:02:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
