Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.31,1:03:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.66,1:04:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.33,1:04:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,近一点
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.01,1:04:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.68,1:04:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.71,1:04:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,进去了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.58,1:05:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,湿了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.08,1:05:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,湿了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.60,1:05:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,兴奋了
