Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.49,1:06:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.83,1:06:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,舔我的手
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.17,1:06:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,味道怎么样
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.17,1:07:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.67,1:07:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.51,1:07:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.88,1:07:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,舌头伸出来
