Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.87,1:13:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,站起来
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.87,1:13:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.39,1:13:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这个
