Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.75,1:13:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,应该很喜欢吧
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.11,1:14:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.78,1:14:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好
