Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.23,1:24:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,全部
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.23,1:24:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是腰
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.40,1:24:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是因为工作吗
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.06,1:24:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,可能
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.90,1:24:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.90,1:24:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,整天坐办公室
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.23,1:24:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.07,1:24:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.74,1:24:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.24,1:24:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.41,1:24:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不痛吗
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.41,1:24:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,刚好
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.41,1:24:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.59,1:25:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.09,1:25:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.26,1:25:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,能用力点吗
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.76,1:25:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.10,1:25:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,真好
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.78,1:25:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,您睡眠不足吗
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.78,1:25:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,睡眠时间真的不够
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.95,1:25:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.30,1:25:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,睡眠不足有害健康
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.14,1:25:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,今天不用上班吗
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.31,1:25:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,也要工作的
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.31,1:25:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那我好好帮您
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.81,1:26:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.66,1:26:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这里好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.05,1:27:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你工作也会累吧
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.22,1:27:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是的啊
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.89,1:27:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.56,1:27:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.26,1:27:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.44,1:28:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,涂点精油
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.44,1:28:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.95,1:28:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.12,1:28:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.96,1:28:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.80,1:28:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,腿可以张开吗
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.14,1:28:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.64,1:28:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.14,1:28:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.67,1:29:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,腿可以抬起来吗
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.84,1:29:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.67,1:29:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.34,1:29:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.87,1:29:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来是精油按摩
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.88,1:29:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.22,1:30:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.39,1:30:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.06,1:30:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,真舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.06,1:30:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.23,1:30:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这里很重要
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.92,1:30:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这样舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.43,1:30:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.65,1:31:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这里也舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.66,1:31:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,超级舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.66,1:31:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.83,1:31:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,拿掉吗
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.00,1:31:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.84,1:31:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.17,1:31:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.85,1:32:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,手可以张开吗
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.35,1:32:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.02,1:32:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢配合
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.52,1:32:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我来服务您
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.03,1:32:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.04,1:32:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这里也要吗
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.21,1:32:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.04,1:32:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,每次都要的
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.71,1:32:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,有点那个
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.05,1:32:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这样才对全身的放松有效果
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.72,1:32:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,也是项目的内容吗
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.89,1:32:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是的包含在内
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.40,1:32:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.56,1:32:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.74,1:33:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我有点害羞
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.08,1:33:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.41,1:33:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,可以不用
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.91,1:33:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不过这也是我们的特色
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.59,1:33:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,请体验
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.59,1:33:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.59,1:33:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.59,1:33:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不会
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.43,1:33:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,硬起来了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.76,1:33:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是感到舒服的证据啊
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.94,1:33:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.95,1:33:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这里不放松对身体不好的
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.12,1:33:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.62,1:33:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.79,1:34:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我没骗你的
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.63,1:34:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.82,1:34:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,还要这样吗
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.82,1:34:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.84,1:34:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,犬家都这样做吗
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.01,1:34:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.84,1:34:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是重要部位
Dialogue: 0,1:34:52.34,1:34:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.69,1:35:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚刚说全身疲惫
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.69,1:35:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.86,1:35:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这样做才有效果
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.22,1:35:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不过这样的话好像快射了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.06,1:35:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这样不好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.39,1:35:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,完全没关系
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.06,1:35:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,射了也没事
Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.41,1:36:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.91,1:36:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.61,1:36:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来是身体按摩
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.79,1:36:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.29,1:36:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你要脱吗
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.63,1:36:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.13,1:36:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.63,1:36:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这也是项目的内容之一
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.97,1:37:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,请允许我服务
